        </div>
        <div class="pcard-body">
          <span class="pcard-brand">Neuriva</span>
          <h3 class="pcard-name">Brain Performance Gummies</h3>
          <div class="pcard-stars">
            <span class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
            <span class="rating-val">4.6</span>
            <span class="review-ct">(12,450 reviews)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-specs">
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Key Ingredients</strong><span>Neurofactor + Phosphatidylserine</span></div>
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Dose</strong><span>100mg Neurofactor + 100mg PS</span></div>
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Servings</strong><span>50 per container</span></div>
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Testing</strong><span>Third-party tested, Decaffeinated</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-price">
            <span class="price">$32.99</span>
            <span class="per-serv">$0.66/serving</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-pros-cons">
            <div class="pcard-pros">
              <h3>Pros</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Neurofactor clinically shown to increase BDNF levels by 143%</li>
                <li>Phosphatidylserine backed by FDA-qualified health claim</li>
                <li>Highest review count of any brain gummy on Amazon (12,450+)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="pcard-cons">
              <h3>Cons</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>PS dose (100mg) is below the 300mg used in most clinical trials</li>
                <li>Contains added sugars (3g per serving)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-ctas">
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Neuriva+Brain+Performance+Gummies&tag=gummyguidepro-20" class="btn-cta" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener" target="_blank">Check Price on Amazon</a>
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Neuriva+brain+gummies&tag=gummyguidepro-20" class="btn-amazon" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener" target="_blank">Compare Options</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Neuriva earns the top spot as the most well-rounded brain gummy available in 2026. The proprietary Neurofactor ingredient, derived from whole coffee cherry extract, has been clinically demonstrated to increase brain-derived neurotrophic factor (BDNF) by 143% in a controlled trial. BDNF is critical for neuroplasticity, the brain's ability to form new neural connections essential for learning and memory. Combined with phosphatidylserine, a phospholipid that supports cell membrane integrity in neurons, this is a dual-mechanism formula with genuine scientific backing. The 100mg PS dose is lower than the 300mg typically used in clinical studies, but Neuriva compensates with the Neurofactor synergy. With over 12,000 verified reviews and the strongest brand recognition in the brain supplement category, Neuriva is the safest choice for first-time brain gummy users.</p>

      <!-- Product 2: Prevagen Gummies -->
      <div class="pcard">
        <div class="pcard-top">
          <span class="pcard-num">2</span>
          <span class="pcard-badge">Best for Memory</span>
          <img src="/images/products/prevagen-brain-gummies.webp" alt="Prevagen Gummies" width="260" height="260" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="pcard-body">
          <span class="pcard-brand">Prevagen</span>
          <h3 class="pcard-name">Memory Support Gummies</h3>
          <div class="pcard-stars">
            <span class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
            <span class="rating-val">4.5</span>
            <span class="review-ct">(8,920 reviews)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-specs">
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Key Ingredients</strong><span>Apoaequorin + Vitamin D</span></div>
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Dose</strong><span>10mg Apoaequorin</span></div>
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Servings</strong><span>30 per container</span></div>
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Testing</strong><span>Madison Memory Study</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-price">
            <span class="price">$39.95</span>
            <span class="per-serv">$1.33/serving</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-pros-cons">
            <div class="pcard-pros">
              <h3>Pros</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Unique apoaequorin protein supports calcium regulation in brain cells</li>
                <li>The #1 pharmacist-recommended memory supplement brand</li>
                <li>Backed by the Madison Memory Study, a double-blind clinical trial</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="pcard-cons">
              <h3>Cons</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Most expensive per serving on this list ($1.33)</li>
                <li>Limited independent research beyond the proprietary Madison Study</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-ctas">
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Prevagen+brain+gummies&tag=gummyguidepro-20" class="btn-cta" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener" target="_blank">Check Price on Amazon</a>
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Prevagen+gummies+memory&tag=gummyguidepro-20" class="btn-amazon" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener" target="_blank">Compare Options</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Prevagen is the most recognized memory supplement brand in the United States, and its gummy format extends that legacy to a wider audience. The active ingredient, apoaequorin, is a protein originally found in jellyfish that supports calcium regulation within brain cells. Excess intracellular calcium is a key driver of age-related cognitive decline, and apoaequorin helps maintain healthy calcium levels in neurons. The proprietary Madison Memory Study, a 90-day double-blind placebo-controlled trial, reported improvements in memory recall within 90 days. While some experts have questioned the independence of this research, Prevagen's 8,900+ reviews and pharmacist recommendation status reflect strong real-world satisfaction. At $1.33 per serving, this is a premium choice best suited for adults over 50 specifically targeting memory preservation.</p>

      <!-- Product 3: Nature's Way Brain Builder Gummies -->
      <div class="pcard">
        <div class="pcard-top">
          <span class="pcard-num">3</span>
          <span class="pcard-badge">Best for Kids</span>
