            </div>
            <div class="pcard-cons">
              <h3>Cons</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>DHA dose (100mg) is lower than standalone fish oil supplements</li>
                <li>Not designed for adult cognitive enhancement</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-ctas">
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Natures+Way+Brain+Builder+Gummies&tag=gummyguidepro-20" class="btn-cta" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener" target="_blank">Check Price on Amazon</a>
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Nature+Way+brain+gummies+kids&tag=gummyguidepro-20" class="btn-amazon" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener" target="_blank">Compare Options</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Nature's Way Brain Builder is the standout option for parents seeking cognitive support for school-age children. The formula centers on omega-3 DHA, the essential fatty acid that constitutes approximately 25% of the brain's total fat content and is critical for neural development, learning, and attention during childhood. The addition of choline and B vitamins further supports neurotransmitter production. At $0.37 per serving, this is also the most affordable brain gummy in our ranking by a significant margin. Nature's Way has earned NSF certification, which means every batch is independently verified for potency and purity. The limitation is clear: this is a pediatric formula, so adults looking for nootropic-level cognitive enhancement should look elsewhere on this list.</p>

      <!-- Product 4: Force Factor Brain Health Gummies -->
      <div class="pcard">
        <div class="pcard-top">
          <span class="pcard-num">4</span>
          <span class="pcard-badge">Best Value</span>
          <img src="/images/products/force-factor-brain-gummies.webp" alt="Force Factor Brain Health Gummies" width="260" height="260" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="pcard-body">
          <span class="pcard-brand">Force Factor</span>
          <h3 class="pcard-name">Brain Health Gummies</h3>
          <div class="pcard-stars">
            <span class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9734;</span>
            <span class="rating-val">4.4</span>
            <span class="review-ct">(5,670 reviews)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-specs">
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Key Ingredients</strong><span>Phosphatidylserine + B12 + Huperzine A</span></div>
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Dose</strong><span>100mg PS + B Vitamins</span></div>
