          </div>
          <div class="pcard-price">
            <span class="price">$19.99</span>
            <span class="per-serv">$0.33/serving</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-pros-cons">
            <div class="pcard-pros">
              <h3>Pros</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Best value for adults at $0.33 per serving with 60 servings per bottle</li>
                <li>Huperzine A inhibits acetylcholinesterase for acetylcholine support</li>
                <li>Available at Walmart and Amazon for easy access</li>
