            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-ctas">
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Force+Factor+Brain+Health+Gummies&tag=gummyguidepro-20" class="btn-cta" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener" target="_blank">Check Price on Amazon</a>
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Force+Factor+brain+gummies&tag=gummyguidepro-20" class="btn-amazon" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener" target="_blank">Compare Options</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Force Factor delivers the best price-to-quality ratio for adults seeking daily brain support without premium pricing. At $0.33 per serving with a 60-count bottle, this is the most economical adult brain gummy in our ranking. The formula includes phosphatidylserine for membrane health, B12 for neural energy metabolism, and huperzine A, a compound derived from Chinese club moss that inhibits the enzyme responsible for breaking down acetylcholine. Acetylcholine is the neurotransmitter most directly linked to memory formation and recall. Force Factor's wide retail distribution through Walmart and Amazon makes it the most accessible option for shoppers who prefer to buy in-store. The trade-off is a proprietary blend format that prevents dose verification of individual ingredients.</p>

      <!-- Product 5: Goli Matcha Mind Cognitive Gummies -->
      <article class="pcard" id="goli-matcha-mind-gummies">
        <div class="pcard-top">
          <img src="/images/products/goli-matcha-mind.webp" alt="Goli Matcha Mind Cognitive Gummies bottle" width="260" height="260" loading="lazy" />
