          </div>
          <div class="pcard-specs">
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Key Ingredient</strong><span>Cognizin® Citicoline 250mg + Matcha 100mg</span></div>
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Dosage</strong><span>3 gummies daily</span></div>
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Servings</strong><span>20 per container</span></div>
