              <h3>Pros</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Cognizin® citicoline is the most clinically studied nootropic compound with 20+ trials</li>
                <li>Matcha provides L-theanine + caffeine for calm, sustained focus without jitters</li>
                <li>Branded ingredient (Cognizin®) ensures standardized potency and purity</li>
